entry.title: CuteNfuzzy Professional Heavy Duty Pet Nail Clipper with Nail File
entry.summary:
Vendor: cuteNfuzzy
Type: Pet Grooming
Price: 7.95

Keep your pets nails a healthy length with these nail clippers. Handle is made of TPE and PP which are environmentally friendly materials - helps protect people and pets with skin allergies. Stainless steel blades are polished and nickel-plated, sharp and durable. A nail file at the end of the handle is used to trim the nail after cutting. A safety lock allows you to lock the clipper when it's not in use.
  • Stainless steel blades are polished and nickel-plated
  • Movable safety shield is installed on the blades to prevent over cutting.
  • Spring devices between the handles allow smooth cutting and trimming
  • A nail file at the end of the handle is used to trim the nail after cutting
  • The handle is made of TPE and PP which are environmentally friendly materials. This helps protect people and pets with skin allergies.
